spec_data.Name: snmpcheck
spec_data.Description:
snmpcheck supports the following enumerations:
   * Contact
   * Description
   * Devices
   * Domain
   * Hardware and storage information
   * Hostname
   * IIS statistics
   * IP forwarding
   * Listening UDP ports
   * Location
   * Motd
   * Mountpoints
   * Network interfaces
   * Network services
   * Processes
   * Routing information
   * Software components (Windows programs or RPMs etc.)
   * System Uptime
   * TCP connections
   * Total Memory
   * Uptime
   * User accounts
   * Web server information (IIS)
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 06:30:09 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: An utility to get information via SNMP protocols
